Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Knowledge=The Excellence of Wisdom
By: Sri Chandrasekhara Bhârati Swâmigal
---
That alone is entitled to the name of knowledge which makes clear to us the
nature of the Self and gets us the everlasting bliss of Freedom.
